## Obtenir l'Auth Code del domini [/authcode]

Podràs consultar l'Auth Code de qualsevol dels teus dominis.

Retorna `response`

### POST | Get Domain Authcode [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Accept: application/json
            apikey: <APIKEY>

    + Body

            {"data": {"domain": "<DOMAIN>","action":"get"}}

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "status": "ok",
          "data": {
            "msg": "Authcode obtained successfully",
            "result": {
              "authcode": "xxxxxxxx"
            }
          }
        }

+ Response 500 (application/json)

        {
          "status": "ko",
          "data": "THE AUTHCODE FOR test.com IS NOT AVAILABLE"
        }

---

## Llistar dominis [/domains/list]

Podràs obtenir un llistat dels teus dominis amb tota la informació associada a ells o només amb els noms de domini.

Tingues en compte que serà necessari enviar el paràmetre `extended_info` amb valor 1 si vols obtenir tota la informació relativa a cada domini, o el valor 0 en el cas que només vulguis obtenir els noms de dominis.

Retorna `response`

### POST | Get Domains List [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Accept: application/json
            apikey: <APIKEY>

    + Body

            {"data": {"extended_info": 1}}

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "status": "ok",
          "data": {
            "msg": "Domain list with extended info for client apidedominios",
            "result": [
              {
                "domain": "test.com",
                "contacts": {
                  "owner": {
                    "name": "Test owner",
                    "email": "test@test.com",
                    "phone": "+34.935769241"
                  },
                  "administrative": {
                    "name": "Test Admin",
                    "email": "test@test.com",
                    "phone": "+34.935769241"
                  },
                  "billing": {
                    "name": "Test Billing",
                    "email": "test@test.com",
                    "phone": "+34.935769241"
                  },
                  "technical": {
                    "name": "Test Tech",
                    "email": "test@test.com",
                    "phone": "+34.935769241"
                  }
                },
                "registration_date": "27/10/2016",
                "expiration_date": "27/12/2022",
                "dns_zones": [
                  "ns1.cdmon.net",
                  "ns2.cdmon.net",
                  "ns3.cdmon.net"
                ],
                "autorenew": false
              }
            ]
          }
        }

+ Response 500 (application/json)

        {
          "status": "ko",
          "data": "USER NOT FOUND"
        }

