## Transferència de domini [/transfer]

Pots realitzar peticions de transferència a **cdmon**. Per a això, serà necessari que el domini no tingui l'estat EPP en *transferProhibited* i que l'Auth Code sigui correcte.

Retorna `response`

### POST | Domain transfer [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Accept: application/json
            User-Agent: resellertool documentation
            apikey: <APIKEY>

    + Body

            {"data": {"domain": "<DOMAIN>", "authcode": "<AUTHCODE>"}}

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "status": "ok",
          "data": {
            "msg": "Transfer request of domain <DOMAIN> finished successfully",
            "result": {
              "transferRequested": true
            }
          }
        }

+ Response 403 (application/json)

        {
          "status": "error",
          "message": "Not enough balance"
        }

+ Response 500 (application/json)

        {
          "status": "error",
          "data": {
            "code": "EPP_EXPIRED_DATE_FOA",
            "msg": "THE DOMAIN CANNOT BE TRANSFERRED. TRANSFER MUST START AT LEAST 7 DAYS PRIOR TO THE DOMAIN EXPIRATION DATE"
          }
        }

