Per a més informació sobre les particularitats, visita l'apartat [*particularitats d'enviar DNS Key*](https://apidedominios.docs.apiary.io/reference/particularidades-de-send-dns-key) d'aquesta documentació.

Retorna `response`

### POST | Send Dns Key [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Accept: application/json
            apikey: P5uDiZaq0qmchH3nCF6ShDR7VtlZhqL6

    + Body

            {"data": {"domain": "wiseroad.eu", "type": "key", "algorithm": 14, "flags": 257, "pubKey": "<PUBKEY>"}}

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "status": "ok",
          "data": "DNS Key was sended to the provider!"
        }

+ Response 500 (application/json)

        {
          "status": "ko",
          "data": "error"
        }

