# Group Particularitats d'enviar DNS Key

## Valors permesos per a algorithm

| Algorismes         | Valor |
|--------------------|-------|
| RSAMD5             | 1     |
| DH                 | 2     |
| DSA-SHA-1          | 3     |
| RSASHA1            | 5     |
| DSA-NSEC3-SHA1     | 6     |
| RSA SHA1-NSEC3-SHA | 7     |
| RSASHA256          | 8     |
| RSASHA512          | 10    |
| ECC-GOST           | 12    |
| ECDSA Curve P-256  | 13    |
| ECDSA Curve P-384  | 14    |
| ed25519            | 15    |
| ed448              | 16    |
| PRIVATEDNS         | 253   |
| PRIVATEOID         | 254   |

## Valors permesos per a digest type

| Algorismes | Valor |
|------------|-------|
| SHA-1      | 1     |
| SHA-256    | 2     |
| SHA-384    | 4     |

## Valors permesos per a flags

| Algorismes | Valor |
|------------|-------|
| ZSK        | 256   |
| KSK        | 257   |

